<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>How do I rent a bike?</strong>
        <p>To rent a bike, simply browse our selection, choose the station you want, and follow the easy steps to complete the rental process.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>What are the rental rates?</strong>
        <p>Our rental rates vary based on the duration of your rental. Check our pricing page for detailed information on hourly and daily rates.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>Is there a minimum age requirement for renting a bike?</strong>
        <p>Yes, there is a minimum age requirement for renting a bike is 16 years old.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>What happens if the bike is damaged during my rental?</strong>
        <p>If the bike is damaged during your rental, please report it immediately. Charges may apply based on the extent of the damage.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <strong>What forms of payment do you accept?</strong>
        <p>We accept major credit cards and debit cards as forms of payment.</p>
    </li>
</ul>



